  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine if black cohosh extract (BCE) administration in
      symptomatic postmenopausal women results in estrogenic stimulation of the breast, as
      determined by estradiol, pS2, FSH, LH, and PSA levels in nipple aspirate fluid.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
